      *
           MOVE    ZERO                TO  WRK-PAGE
           MOVE    ZERO                TO  WRK-LINE
           MOVE    ZERO                TO  IDX-L
           INITIALIZE                  HC15
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX     FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL       IDX     >   200
               ADD     1               TO  IDX-L
               IF      IDX-L           >   33
      *            帳票印刷開始処理
                   PERFORM 200-HC15-PRINT-SEC
                   ADD     1           TO  IDX-L
               END-IF
               MOVE    ZERO                TO  FLG-SYORI
               PERFORM VARYING     IDY     FROM    1   BY  1
                       UNTIL       IDY     >   6
                   IF      SPA-GMN-TKNJNAME(IDY IDX)
                                           NOT =   SPACE
                       MOVE    1               TO  FLG-SYORI
      *                明細編集処理
                       PERFORM 300-HC15-HEN-SEC
                   END-IF
               END-PERFORM
      *
               IF      FLG-SYORI           =   ZERO
                   MOVE    200             TO  IDX
               END-IF
      *
           END-PERFORM
      *
           IF      IDX-L           >   ZERO
      *        帳票印刷開始処理
               PERFORM 200-HC15-PRINT-SEC
           END-IF
      *
           .
